Asteroids by Brandon Son

Use the 'W' key to move forward in the direction you are facing. 
Press 'A' to rotate left, press 'D' to rotate right.
Press Shift to randomly teleport to another location on the screen
But beware of randomly teloporting into asteroids.
Press Space to shoot.

Do not get hit by the asteroids, if you do you lose a life. 
Lives are displayed in the top left corner.

Accumulate the most points you can by shooting the asteroids.
Large Asteroids = 1000 points.
Medium Asteroids = 2000 points.
Large Asteroids = 3000 points.
Final score is shown after the game is over.




